<div class = 'img'><a href = 'http://www.drdobbs.com/joltawards/jolt-awards-the-best-books/240162065?pgno=2'><img src = 'http://martinfowler.com/nosql.jpg' width = '75' height = '' alt = '' title = ''/></a></div><p>I’m chuffed to see that <a href="http://martinfowler.com/books/nosql.html">NoSQL Distilled</a> won an award today - as a finalist in Dr Dobb’s Jolt Awards, marking it as one of their top 5 books of the year. This is the third book I’ve written that’s got this kind of award and Pramod’s <a href="http://martinfowler.com/books/refactoringDatabases.html">second award</a> (but he’s written less so has a higher average). </p>
